</center></div></div><div class="panel-separator"></div><div class="panel-pane pane-block pane-ns-forum-block-ns-forum-block pane-ns-forum-block" ><h2 class="pane-title"> Forum discussions</h2><div class="pane-content"><div class = "border-box"><div class="twitter-timeline-link"><a href="https://www.thenakedscientists.com/forum/index.php?topic=77918" class="fa fa-comments-o ajax-exclude" style="font-size: 2em; color: #5aad8b;" aria-hidden="true"></a><a href="https://www.thenakedscientists.com/forum/index.php?topic=77918" class="twitter-timeline-link ajax-exclude" style="color: #111; font-size: 1em;"> why do a lot of people confuse between interference and diffraction?</a><br><br><a href="https://www.thenakedscientists.com/forum/index.php?topic=86906" class="fa fa-comments-o ajax-exclude" style="font-size: 2em; color: #5aad8b;" aria-hidden="true"></a><a href="https://www.thenakedscientists.com/forum/index.php?topic=86906" class="twitter-timeline-link ajax-exclude" style="color: #111; font-size: 1em;"> QotW - 24.05.10 - Why is new plastic flexible but old plastic brittle?</a><br><br><a href="https://www.thenakedscientists.com/forum/index.php?topic=86694" class="fa fa-comments-o ajax-exclude" style="font-size: 2em; color: #5aad8b;" aria-hidden="true"></a><a href="https://www.thenakedscientists.com/forum/index.php?topic=86694" class="twitter-timeline-link ajax-exclude" style="color: #111; font-size: 1em;"> What is the Hopf gauge?</a><br><br><a href="https://www.thenakedscientists.com/forum/index.php?topic=86899" class="fa fa-comments-o ajax-exclude" style="font-size: 2em; color: #5aad8b;" aria-hidden="true"></a><a href="https://www.thenakedscientists.com/forum/index.php?topic=86899" class="twitter-timeline-link ajax-exclude" style="color: #111; font-size: 1em;"> Does regenerative braking have a hazardous complication?</a><br></div></div><br></div></div><div class="panel-separator"></div><div class="panel-pane pane-views pane-featured-content" ><h2 class="pane-title"> Featured</h2><div class="pane-content"><div class="view view-featured-content view-id-featured_content view-display-id-block_1 view-dom-id-78cbc519200b15d911e9c8abcf5c34f4"><div class="view-content"><div class="views-row views-row-1 views-row-odd views-row-first"><div class="views-field views-field-nothing"> <span class="field-content"><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-3"><a href="/podcasts/naked-scientists-podcast/astrazeneca-covid-vaccine-clots-and-self-eating-plastic"><img typeof="foaf:Image" class="img-responsive" src="https://www.thenakedscientists.com/sites/default/files/styles/media_thumbnail/public/media/media/53e1dc4b4956ab14f6da8c7dda7930791439dbed534c704f75277bd79e49cd5c_1280.jpg?itok=dqlB02C4" width="100" height="100" alt="A syringe sticking out of a globe, lying on a facemask." title="A syringe sticking out of a globe, lying on a facemask." /></a></div><div class="col-xs-9"><div class="views-field-title"><a href="/podcasts/naked-scientists-podcast/astrazeneca-covid-vaccine-clots-and-self-eating-plastic">AstraZeneca Covid vaccine clots, and self eating plastic</a></div><div class="views-field-term-node-tid"><a href="/podcasts/naked-scientists-podcast">The Naked Scientists Podcast</a></div></div></div></span></div></div><div class="views-row views-row-2 views-row-even"><div class="views-field views-field-nothing"> <span class="field-content"><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-3"><a href="/podcasts/naked-scientists-podcast/how-survive-space"><img typeof="foaf:Image" class="img-responsive" src="https://www.thenakedscientists.com/sites/default/files/styles/media_thumbnail/public/media/media/images/g552a80c712d56bd9f059c3dd18d06e52d4d3a08800fec824cd18adf9a47aca6c7b60a11d972f8042d3f19a6e27cd8b6ceaa137c475ef43fd01beca87b1b47b03_1280.jpg?itok=c9aYGobf" width="100" height="100" alt="Space flight" title="Space flight" /></a></div><div class="col-xs-9"><div class="views-field-title"><a href="/podcasts/naked-scientists-podcast/how-survive-space">How to survive in s